Package: bvpSolve
Version: 1.1
Title: Solvers for boundary value problems of ordinary differential equations
Author: Karline Soetaert <k.soetaert@nioo.knaw.nl>,
        Jeff Cash <j.cash@imperial.ac.uk>
Maintainer: Karline Soetaert <k.soetaert@nioo.knaw.nl>
Depends: R (>= 2.01), rootSolve, deSolve
Description: Functions that solve boundary value problems (BVP) of systems of ordinary
             differential equations (ODE).
             The functions provide an interface to the FORTRAN function
             twpbvp and an R-implementation of the shooting method.
License: GPL (>= 2)
LazyData: yes

